Package com.jgraph.layout.organic

Class Summary
JGraphFastOrganicLayout This layout is an implementation of "Graph Drawing by Force-Directed Placement" by Fruchterman and Reingold (1991).
JGraphOrganicLayout An implementation of a simulated annealing layout, based on "Drawing Graphs Nicely Using Simulated Annealing" by Davidson and Harel (1996).
JGraphSelfOrganizingOrganicLayout This layout is an implementation of inverted self-organising maps as described by Bernd Meyer in his 1998 paper "Self-Organizing Graphs - A Neural Network Perspective of Graph Layout".
